Author: Alexfrog#1338
Content: The biggest trick to learning to trade is to not believe all the bullshit "if it goes up it goes up more, and if it goes down it goes down more" TA.

Author: Alexfrog#1338
Content: That is all made to trick noobs into buying after a rise and selling after a drop.

Author: Alexfrog#1338
Content: Instead, sell the rise and buy the drop

Author: Alexfrog#1338
Content: Also dont daytrade.
